{"name":"Alchemy","type":"ability","img":"modules/hyperborea-content/assets/icons/ability.png","system":{"description":"<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 29\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>To practice the sorcery-science of alchemy. Apprentice cryomancers learn how to identify potions by taste alone; albeit the practice is not always safe. At 7th level, a cryomancer may concoct potions with the assistance of an alchemist. By 11th level, the assistance of an alchemist is no longer required. For more information, refer to <strong>Chapter 7: Sorcery</strong>, <em>alchemy</em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"transparent","requirements":"cryomancer","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false,"tags":[]},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"hyperborea","systemVersion":"1.000","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679250807770,"modifiedTime":1681579230717,"lastModifiedBy":"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea"},"_id":"iPWkkv7WnyUR7Nbk","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea":3}}
